ything is good.\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small tear\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"my upper trap\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am lucky to have amazing doctors and physios in the national team.\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing doctors\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1458}, {\"ngram\": \"physios\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1470}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are doing everything we can.\", \"from\": 1494, \"to\": 1526, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have had a great, great camp and I am in fantastic shape.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great, great camp\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1557}, {\"ngram\": \"fantastic shape\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"May the best three guys win on the day.\\\"\", \"from\": 1587, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best three guys\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1610}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1625}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the third oldest male swimmer at these Games, so in those terms I am something of a pensioner,\\\" Le Clos toldTeam South Africa.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the third oldest male swimmer\", \"from\": 1635, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1679}, {\"ngram\": \"those terms\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1713}, {\"ngram\": \"a pensioner\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1728}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And in spite of picking up a shoulder tear in training, I have come to Paris believing I have a chance.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1835, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999972483238, \"rank\": 2.7518064179925782e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spite\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"a shoulder tear\", \"from\": 1791, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1818}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have raced with injuries before.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1902, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1894}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think that the semi-final will be the harder race, because there will be 16 swimmers going for a place in the final.\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the harder race\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"16 swimmers\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"the final\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2022}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am hoping to get there and once I do I will be chasing another dream.\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2095, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another dream\", \"from\": 2081, \"to\": 2094}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a warrior, a born racer.\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a warrior\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"a born racer\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, I have had an injury the last two weeks.\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an injury\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I went to the medical team as soon as I arrived from Montpellier and had it checked out.\